  <div id="text-content_a846087b-53af-459c-9f73-3ae2227f5204" class="text-block-content">
    <p>You can create rubrics for instructors to use across your institution. Instructors can add account-level rubrics to their assignments, graded discussions, and quizzes. Instructors can also create their own rubrics in their courses.</p>
  </div>
</div>

      <div class="step screensteps-section screensteps-depth-1" id="open_account" data-step-uuid="4c0272db-2654-4354-a9ac-eaee63d5193b">
    <h2 id="open_account" class="step-title screensteps-heading">Open Account</h2>
        <div class="image screensteps-image">
      <img src="https://media.screensteps.com/image_assets/assets/007/949/740/original/167b4d34-2e3f-4046-9aed-39673e67bdab.png" srcset="" alt="Open Account" height="542" width="453">
  </div>
 
      <div class="step-instructions screensteps-textblock">
  <div id="text-content_4b86a6a5-ce33-4247-a8f4-f083cff1cd0a" class="text-block-content">
    <p>In Global Navigation, click the <strong>Admin</strong> link [1], then click the name of the account [2].</p>
  </div>
</div>
 
  </div>

      <div class="step screensteps-section screensteps-depth-1" id="open_rubrics" data-step-uuid="d4c96fa5-2aae-471c-8a45-759b947777a1">
    <h2 id="open_rubrics" class="step-title screensteps-heading">Open Rubrics</h2>
        <div class="image screensteps-image">
      <img src="https://media.screensteps.com/image_assets/assets/005/797/317/original/e33aa415-8ae7-4fe4-9df1-711fdb55ebbd.png" srcset="" alt="Open Rubrics" height="305" width="155">
  </div>
 
      <div class="step-instructions screensteps-textblock">
  <div id="text-content_d4da792f-ab80-4cfb-ab69-dc963923e99a" class="text-block-content">
    <p>In Account Navigation, click the <strong>Rubrics</strong> link.</p>
  </div>
</div>
 
  </div>

      <div class="step screensteps-section screensteps-depth-1" id="add_rubric" data-step-uuid="245a920c-3922-4194-a8c7-1f4dc0b15d12">
    <h2 id="add_rubric" class="step-title screensteps-heading">Add Rubric</h2>
        <div class="image screensteps-image">
      <img src="https://media.screensteps.com/image_assets/assets/001/735/290/original/d40c7198-abef-4291-9d1c-433e0fb5200e.png" srcset="" alt="Add Rubric" height="77" width="278">
  </div>
 
      <div class="step-instructions screensteps-textblock">
  <div id="text-content_45747849-6ffc-43eb-9e7b-7cb62e8f1ff1" class="text-block-content">
    <p>Click the <strong>Add Rubric</strong> button.</p>
  </div>
</div>
 
        <div class="step screensteps-section screensteps-depth-2" id="create_title" data-step-uuid="2b37da89-8616-4939-b344-fe998c1f67e5">
    <h3 id="create_title" class="step-title screensteps-heading">Add Details</h3>
        <div class="image screensteps-image">
      <img src="https://media.screensteps.com/image_assets/assets/001/735/282/original/e63ccb8d-c7d6-437e-ba04-cb79e78476b2.png" srcset="" alt="Create Title" height="307" width="798">
  </div>
 
